snippet.title: Classic Fun Collection 5 in 1 - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
The Classic Fun Collection is a pack of 5 games in 1 for you to enjoy!

G-Tris: a close friend of Tetris
Pirate Solitaire: play the Solitaire in the universe of pirates
Mahjong: the mythical chinese game
Sudoku: a must-have!
Bayou words: try to find as many words as possible with the few letters available

Developed by 3DDUO
Published by Plug In Digital / Fun4Family
